{"type": "article", "id": 2823, "title": "专为 iPhone 6 打造的手机折叠钱包", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-14T09:30:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232235cRwznd1xf5HrF8JI.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自英国的配件品牌 Hard Graft 近来持续推出新品，此番又带来了一款专为 iPhone 6 打造的手机折叠钱包，设计上采用了意大利产的深蓝色皮革构成外壳，搭配以品牌标志性的 X 白色缝线形成对比，内部则利用毛毡物料结合黑色植鞣皮革制作而成，除了可以放入一部 iPhone 6 之外，还可以存放零钱与银行卡等小物件。定价 109 英镑，<a href=\"http://www.hardgraft.com/collections/ocean/products/mightyphonefoldwallet-ocean\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232233J8gn0lS95HNrG1sK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052322344tOoCBelT17YUSPM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232234SA7czNbo25kJBuis.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}